Keterangan Perhitungan & Warna:

Rumus Perhitungan:
  • TW (Turnover Weeks) = Stock WH / Avg Sales 3 Bulan
  • TO (Turnover) = Stock Toko / Avg Sales 3 Bulan
  • TW+TO = Total Stock / Avg Sales 3 Bulan
Arti Warna TW/TO:
<1 Critical 1-2 Low 2-4 Normal >4 High
Arti Warna TW+TO:
<2 Critical 2-4 Low 4-8 Normal >8 High
